09:36.409 --> 09:38.646
Okay, let go, God damn it.

09:43.050 --> 09:44.918
Oh, shit.

09:48.555 --> 09:49.757
Son of a bitch.

09:49.823 --> 09:51.258
Look, I don't know who did this,

09:51.324 --> 09:52.392
