all this stuff.

09:53.794 --> 09:54.995
Yeah, I know that, Marva.

09:55.062 --> 09:57.164
The model at Ryan's
and the blueprints,

09:57.230 --> 09:58.165
where are they?

09:58.231 --> 09:59.466
