36:03.229 --> 36:05.231
and I will reveal
what I know to be true.

36:05.297 --> 36:07.299
I will be a whistleblower,

36:07.366 --> 36:10.936
and then I will sue you both
for wrongful termination,

36:11.002 --> 36:12.037
and I'll win, too.

36:12.103 --> 36:14.406
God. y-you know what?

36:14.473 --> 36:17.243
